8. Mendez, P. L. (2024). The Empirical Validation of Recursive Feedback in Neural Network Architectures.
 Contribution: Explores how recursive feedback enables adaptive and scalable intelligence. This work validates the operational framework of FractiScope, emphasizing its capability to handle complex, layered systems.
9. LeCun, Y., Bengio, Y., & Hinton, G. (2015). Deep Learning. Nature, 521(7553), 436–444.
 Contribution: Outlines the structured problem-solving capabilities of deep learning systems, supporting FractiPower’s categorization of AI systems.
